body:
The title pretty much explains it all.

This thread is for members to post in there opinion who the Top 10 Walls players are of all time.

Remember it is he/she's opinion please don't give hate to a person on how they rank you or even rank you at all.

So here's my Top 10.

1. Polar_Express
2. 99250
3.Patrikano 
4.Meggs And Bacon
5.Porcupine
6.Tobin
7.kycraft
8.Coco Debby
9.Rilo
10.morganroths

Now I'm interested to see what the rest of you guys think :D
